功能。请注意，实际路径和命令可能需要根据你的具体环境进行调整。\n\n更多关于Java执行系统命令的信息可以参考[官方文档](https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/lang/Runtime.html#exec-java.lang.String-)。","category":"filesystem","tags":["语音控制","Windows自动化","媒体键模拟","Java执行","本地应用唤醒","MCP语音插件","酷我音乐","快捷指令"],"version":"0.0.0","npmPackage":"mogu520999-mogutongxue-mcp-server","securityScore":60,"requiresApiKey":false,"platforms":["linux","macos","windows"],"isOfficial":false,"isNew":false,"toolCount":0,"installStatus":"not_installed","installable":false,"installMethod":"none","sourceUrl":"https://github.com/mogu520999/mogutongxue","source":"modelscope","configHint":"仅限Windows平台；需确保目标音乐软件已安装且路径正确；部分功能依赖.NET Framework","envSchema":{},"envRequired":[],"isVerified":false,"isHosted":false,"capabilities":["个人语音助手","桌面效率增强","无障碍操作","老年友好交互"]},{"serverId":"@folderr-tech-folderr-mcp-server","friendlyName":"Folderr智能中枢","friendlyNameEn":"folderr助手服务","description":"深度集成Folderr AI助手的MCP服务，支持任务创建、对话状态同步、知识库更新与多模态响应调度，打通AI工作流最后一公里。","descriptionEn":"一个模型上下文协议（MCP）服务器，提供与Folderr API交互的工具，专门用于管理和与[Folderr](https://www.folderr.com/)助手进行通信。","category":"network","tags":["Folderr集成","AI助手协同","任务编排","MCP协议","RAG调度","工作流引擎","国产AI平台","低代码AI"],"version":"0.0.0","npmPackage":"@folderr/folderr-mcp-server","securityScore":60,"requiresApiKey":false,"platforms":["linux","macos","windows"],"isOfficial":false,"isNew":false,"toolCount":0,"installStatus":"not_installed","installable":true,"installMethod":"npm","sourceUrl":"https://github.com/folderr-tech/folderr-mcp-server","source":"modelscope","configHint":"需注册Folderr账号并获取API Token；支持Webhook回调与双向事件流","envSchema":{},"envRequired":[],"isVerified":false,"isHosted":true,"capabilities":["AI客服对接","智能文档助理","会议摘要生成","跨平台Agent协同"]},{"serverId":"stormcloud-math_genie_calc","friendlyName":"数学精灵","friendlyNameEn":"数学精灵计算器","description":"轻量级符号计算与表达式求解工具，支持代数化简、微积分推导、方程求解及可视化图表生成，面向学生与工程师场景。","descriptionEn":"","category":"other","tags":["符号计算","数学求解","教育工具","公式渲染","Matplotlib","SymPy","学习辅助","STEM教学"],"version